Package edu.cmu.cs214.hw5.framework.core

Class RawDataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.cs214.hw5.framework.core.RawDataSet
  • public final class RawDataSet
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of DataPoint objects. This is the common format that all source data must be converted to for use in the framework.
